<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbd6ee80d-47c4-11f1-bea6-82cea744851c" identifier="/us/usc/t31/s5329"><num value="5329">§ 5329.</num><heading> Staff commentaries</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary shall—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idbd6ee80e-47c4-11f1-bea6-82cea744851c" identifier="/us/usc/t31/s5329/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> publish all written rulings interpreting this subchapter; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idbd6ee80f-47c4-11f1-bea6-82cea744851c" identifier="/us/usc/t31/s5329/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> annually issue a staff commentary on the regulations issued under this subchapter.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="idbd6ee810-47c4-11f1-bea6-82cea744851c">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/103/325/tIII/s311/a">Pub. L. 103–325, title III, § 311(a)</ref>, <date date="1994-09-23">Sept. 23, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/2221">108 Stat. 2221</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
